# Aqua Shop Frontend — Project Map

> **Đọc rule này trước** thay vì quét lại toàn bộ source. Root code: `v1/`. Rule file: `v1/.cursor/rules/aqua-shop-structure.mdc`.

## Tech stack

Next.js 16 (App Router) · React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS v4 · Axios · Lucide React · js-cookie

UI text: **tiếng Việt**. Import alias: `@/` → `v1/`. Bo góc nhẹ: card/panel `rounded-xl`, nút/input `rounded-lg`, badge tròn `rounded-full`.

