## Quy ước Next.js routing

| Pattern                        | Ví dụ                                                             | URL                  |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------- |
| Route group `(name)`           | `(auth)/login`                                                    | `/login`             |
| Route group protected          | ~~`(protected)/profile`~~ → `profile/page.tsx` + `useRequireAuth` | `/profile`           |
| Dynamic segment                | `[slug]/page`                                                     | `/ca-canh-thuy-sinh` |
| Static segment                 | `san-pham/[slug]`                                                 | `/san-pham/ten-sp`   |
| ❌ KHÔNG dùng dynamic cho auth | `[auth]/login`                                                    | URL sai              |

**Trên Windows:** không rename `[...]` → `(...)` trực tiếp (EPERM). Tạo folder mới, copy file, xóa cũ bằng `Remove-Item -LiteralPath`.

## Backend & env

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1
API_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8080
NEXT_PUBLIC_PARENT_CATEGORY_SLUGS=ca-canh-thuy-sinh,cay-thuy-sinh,thiet-bi-be-ca
```

Luồng API: component → `@/lib/api.ts` → `axios-client.ts` → `/api/v1/*` → Java backend.

Auth: JWT cookie · auto-refresh 401 · `useAuth()` từ `@/hooks/useAuth`.

**Không dùng mock data.** Không gọi endpoint không tồn tại.

